    <introduction>
      <para>
        DataPorter has its own tray icon on the system tray. You can hide / unhide or close the application window and the tray icon provides access to the application any time it is necessary.
      </para>
      <para>
        Double click on the icon allows us to unhide the application window, right click displays menu that allows to hide/unhide the window and exit the application.
      </para>
